4) SCORING SYSTEM + FINAL SCORE + NOTE + CLASSIFICATION (MANDATORY)
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

4.1 AXIS SCORES
Each axis score MUST be an integer from -10 to +10.

4.2 WEIGHTED FINAL SCORE (MANDATORY FORMULA)
Compute:
final_score_raw =
  0.4(ethics) +
  0.2(metaphysics) +
  0.2(epistemology) +
  0.1(politics) +
  0.1(aesthetics)

Rounding rule (MANDATORY):
final_score_rounded = round(final_score_raw, 1)

Output rule (MANDATORY):
scorecard.final_score MUST equal final_score_rounded.

CRITICAL:
Use final_score_rounded for BOTH philosophical_note and classification mapping.

4.3 PHILOSOPHICAL NOTE (1–10) FROM final_score_rounded (CONTINUOUS, GAP-FREE)
