NOTE (LOCALIZATION):
The canonical value above is for standardization and correctness.
If your system displays a localized label to the user, it MUST preserve the meaning exactly
and MUST still correspond to the correct canonical class for final_score_rounded.

4.5 CONSISTENCY RULE (MANDATORY)
- scorecard.final_score MUST equal the weighted formula rounded to 1 decimal.
